cu.explanation_en: Setting tracking area code to 0 causes invalid TAC, leading to tracking area configuration rejection and mobility issues.

du.explanation_en: Setting PUCCH group hopping to unknown value 5 causes configuration validation failure and cell setup issues.
du.explanation_zh: 將 PUCCH 群組跳頻設定為未知值 5 會導致配置驗證失敗和小區設定問題。
